snippet.title: World Zombination Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Proletariat's first game, World Zombination, is a faction-based real-time strategy game on a global scale available on iOS and Android, and coming to PC and Mac.

http://www.facebook.com/worldzombination
http://www.twitter.com/playzombination
